thi-M%C3%A3-Ph%E1%BB%A5c-Ba/poem-SrtgoD-IfkuOhdlJ5DRxWQ">Ngũ ai thi - Mã Phục Ba - 五哀詩－馬伏波</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C6%B0-M%C3%A3-Quang/author-7OFzGbIEkOgkM6aU4rZZZw">Tư Mã Quang</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Du/Th%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Ng%C3%B4-Tr%C3%BAc-chi-ca-k%E1%BB%B3-15/poem-XEbdlK7rBMtDAT-TTLXr5A">Thương Ngô Trúc chi ca kỳ 15 - 蒼梧竹枝歌其十五</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Du/author-ZRyB2U-4oqfhcjZ7xrf1_A">Nguyễn Du</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-D%E1%BB%A5c-T%C3%BA/T%C3%ADn/poem-mg0J7wkm3ti0EQ-2RTuZ6g">Tín - 信</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-D%E1%BB%A5c-T%C3%BA/author-Q1iBAvdMoGVZdNIyHAuy-w">Lý Dục Tú</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
